Useful bot to expoit the github search box in a large scale

Dependencies:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 - python 2.6
 - mechanize
 - pyquery
 - termcolor


How to use:
~~~~~~~~~~~
 $ python github_bot.py

You have to create a settings file and fill the following variables:
 - github account
    * USERNAME
    * PASSWORD
 - search informations
    * TYPE_SEARCH (e.g. "Users")
    * TYPE_LANGUAGE (e.g. "Python")
    * LOCATION (e.g. "London")
    * PAGE_START (first page to send mail, usually = 1)
    * USER_START (first user of the PAGE_START to send mail, usually = 1)
 - your email
    * SENDER
    * EMAIL_PASSWORD
    * HOST (e.g. smtp.gmail.com)
    * PORT (e.g 587 for google)
 - your message
    * FILE_JOINED (path to the file)
    * MAIL_TITLE
    * MAIL_MESSAGE

